    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>About Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS)</h1>
        <p>
            <!-- introduction to the system and its creator -->
            The Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS) was created by Dianca Jade Naidu to simplify the claim process for Independent Contractor (IC) lecturers. Our goal is to make the process of claim submission, tracking, and approval more efficient, transparent, and user-friendly.
        </p>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2> <!-- statement of the mission -->
        <p>We aim to provide a seamless experience for IC lecturers, reducing the time and effort required to manage monthly claims while ensuring accurate and transparent records.</p>
        <h2>How CMCS Works</h2>    <!-- small overview of how the system functions -->
        <p>CMCS integrates claim submission, document uploads, and tracking functionalities to allow lecturers to manage their claims efficiently. It also offers easy approval workflows for administrators.</p>
